input

Class ParseHardwarePlatform

  • java.lang.Object
    • input.ParseHardwarePlatform

  • public class ParseHardwarePlatform
extends java.lang.Object
    Parse Platfom XML to build a platform model. We first scan and save the information from the XML file. And then build a platform from this information available. This helps to have number of "const" variables in the model, which cannot be altered later on.
    Author:
    Pranav Tendulkar
